CODE ORIGINALLY SOURCED FROM PAN @ CLEF 2025 (Zangerle et al. 2025)

Create results folder in base repo
Evaluation run in CMD / Anaconda Prompt

"
cd path\to\root\repo
python Evaluation/evaluator.py -p predictions -t Data/multiauthor_dataset -o results
"

This outputs proto-text file containing F1 scores for each difficulty. Will also be printed in terminal
